168
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:30,260
You…

169
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:34,660
Let's see if you can still be this sharp-tongued

170
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:36,420
when you go on the animal path

171
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:38,500
